title: Inner CV Axle Puller Tool, CV Axle Puller Tool with 5/8"-18 Slide Hammer and Adapter Slide Hammer Puller Set Front Wheel Drive Axle Pulley Attachment with Outer CV Joint Adapter
features: Package Include: You will receive 1 sliding hammer, 1 constant velocity joint fork (48mm/1.89 inch), 1 constant velocity joint fork (63mm/2.48 inch), 1 outer CV joint adapter (89mm/3.50 inch), 1 manual puller, 2 matching nuts and 1 pair of gloves. This tool set is enough to meet your usage needs.
Product Material: Our CV axle puller tools are made of high strength steel, heat-treated, strong and durable, not easy to break and can be used for a long time.

Product Design: The CV joint puller makes it easier to pull out old stubborn CV axles and install new ones. It won't damage the aluminum gearbox and other parts during use, so you can use it with confidence.

Easy To Use: Our CV axle puller tool is very convenient and practical, threading the constant velocity joint fork removal adapter to the slide hammer, then placing the adapter around the shaft behind the inner shoe. Use a slide hammer to create torque to pull the shaft out.

Wide Application: This CV joint fork has internal threads and the slide hammer bar has external threads. The joint fork can be installed on the slide hammer bar and is suitable for most vehicle models.
